{
  "chapter": 12,
  "chapter_summary": "第十二章\"枫谷春潮\"讲述项少龙与乌廷芳感情突飞猛进的一天。乌廷芳带项少龙走捷径前往牧场，途中二人在枫谷幽潭边发生亲密关系，项少龙借此巩固与乌廷芳的关系并打击情敌连晋。抵达牧场后，乌应元单独与项少龙深谈，考察其出身来历，项少龙谎称为秦人与土女混血后代。乌应元欣赏项少龙的忠义才智，秘密许诺将乌廷芳嫁给他，但要求保密。二人还讨论天下大势，项少龙预言秦国终将统一天下，乌应元对其见识大为赞赏。临别时乌廷芳与项少龙互许终身，项少龙承诺击败连晋后即提亲。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "speaker_name": "乌廷芳",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不用看了！这条是我才知道的捷径，他们是不会向这里来的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "speaker_name": "乌廷芳",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你的胆子真大，从没有男人敢像你那样对我无礼的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "text": "哪里哪里！我只是个胆小鬼吧！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "speaker_name": "乌廷芳",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "骗人家，廷芳一看便知你是不会屈从于任何人的家伙，包括爷爷在内。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "text": "不论你这看法是对是错，绝不可告诉任何人，若传入主人耳内，我定小命不保。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "speaker_name": "乌廷芳",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "看！过了前面的山谷，再经过一座小丘，便可见到牧场的入口。谷内有道美丽的小溪，溪水直流入牧场去。趁阿爹最少还有小半个时辰才到，你要不要向人家多索取点赔偿呢？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "text": "肯放过向你索偿的一定是大呆子、蠢混蛋和疯子。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "speaker_name": "乌廷芳",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你要干什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "text": "这么动人的潭水，不想洗个澡吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "speaker_name": "乌廷芳",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不行啊！弄湿头发，爹定知我们干过什么事，绝不会饶你的。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "text": "我们在浅水处浸浴不就行了？我可保证不弄湿你的秀发。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "speaker_name": "乌廷芳",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "好吧！记得不可弄湿人家的头发，你以为人家不知你真正想的是什么吗？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "speaker_name": "乌廷芳",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "说好是去玩水的嘛！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "text": "我想起没有干布抹身，终是不妥，不若就在这里向你索偿更好，你听瀑布的声音多么悦耳。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "乌应元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "来！让我带少龙四处看看！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "乌应元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "芳儿对少龙很有好感哩！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "乌应元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这也好，我一向不喜欢连晋，此人城府甚深，又和武黑同流合污，只是爹宠信他们，我才拿他们没办法。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "text": "听陶公说，主人有意把孙小姐嫁入王室……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "乌应元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我曾和爹屡次争拗，便是为了此事。爹的年纪大了，看不清目前的形势。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "text": "少主！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "乌应元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙！你老老实实回答我，你究竟是何出身来历，身体内流的是什么血液？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "text": "少主这么看得起少龙，我也不敢隐瞒，其实我乃流落到山区的秦人和土女所生的后代，这事我连陶公都没有明说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "乌应元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "假设我把芳儿许给你，你肯答应一生一世好好爱护她吗？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "text": "可是主人怎肯答应？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "乌应元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "先不要理他的问题。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "乌应元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我欣赏你并非全因你的绝世剑术，又或在对付马贼时显露出来惊人的应变智慧，更重要的是你肯不顾自身，留后抗贼，让战友安全离去。这种对主子忠、对朋友义的做法，才使我放心把芳儿交给你。现在这个只是秘密协议，除陶方外，绝不准透露给第四个人知道，包括芳儿在内。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "text": "少主有什么用得上少龙的地方，尽管吩咐。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "乌应元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "陶方果然没有看错你，只凭你观人于微的心智，将来必是叱咤风云的人物。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "乌应元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "爹真的老了，不知一切形势正在急遽转化中。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "乌应元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "自三晋建侯后，首着先鞭的是三晋赵、魏、韩里的魏文侯。西方的秦、东边的齐、南边的韩、楚，以及北边的赵，没有不受过他的侵略。连邯郸这么坚固的大城池，仍要给他攻破，并占据了达两年之久，若非齐国出头，魏还不肯退兵哩。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "text": "可是后来魏兵被齐国的孙膑大败于马陵，然后秦、齐、赵接连对魏用兵，使其折兵损将，还失去了大片土地，声势已大不如前。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "乌应元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "邯郸没有多少人有你的见地。少龙告诉我，在列强里，你最看好的是哪一个？",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "text": "当然是秦国，最终天下都要臣服于秦人脚下。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "乌应元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我虽看好大秦，却没有你那么肯定。凭什么你会有这个想法？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "text": "关键在于东方诸国是否能合力抗秦，只看目前燕、赵之争，便可知大概。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "乌应元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你说的是'合纵'和'连横'了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "text": "眼下东、南诸国谁愿意维持现状？没有君主不想乘四邻之隙而扩张领土、争取利益，冀能成为天下霸主，所以合纵根本是没有可能的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "乌应元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "幸好你不是我敌人，还是我的未来女婿。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "speaker_name": "乌廷芳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "爹从没有和人谈得这么投契的，少龙真有本领。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "乌应元",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "爹还要去看账目，芳儿陪少龙四处走走！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "speaker_name": "乌廷芳",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "爹看来很喜欢你呢！少龙何时向他提亲，那芳儿可整天磨在你身旁，到时不要讨厌人家才好。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "text": "待我胜过连晋，有了身份地位，立即提亲娶你，怕只怕过不得你爷爷那一关。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "speaker_name": "乌廷芳",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "若爷爷不许，芳儿便死给他看。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "text": "万万不可，最多我和你远走高飞，教他们寻找不着。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "speaker_name": "乌廷芳",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "大丈夫一诺千金，将来绝不能为了舍不得荣华富贵或另有新宠而反悔，芳儿连身体都交了给你，你要一生一世好好珍惜人家啊！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "speaker_name": "乌廷芳",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你小心连晋，他真的很厉害，而且我看他虽或不敢杀你，至少会把你弄成残废方肯罢休。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "text": "放心吧！若连他都斗不赢，哪有资格娶你这天之骄女为妻。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    }
  ],
